  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **The A08 Unifying Principle:** Integrity failures occur whenever code,
  data, or infrastructure is **processed without verifying that it has
  not been tampered with** between the point of creation and the point of
  execution. **Always verify. Never assume.**

